      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CANYA FEEL IT (4) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 0.8 lengths at this track in a handy 23.22 beating Just Johnnie. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. COMPTON ROCKS (1) scored (17.36) last time out at this track adding to an already respectable career. Form here sound including seven wins. Can measure up again. ASTON DEUTZ (2) has some solid form under her belt and proved too strong last time to win by 3 lengths at this track in a handy 17.57 beating Hayden's Milk. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Likely to be in the finish. ROCK IT KATHY (6) won by a wide margin last start. Hard to beat again.",
